headline: Is Now the Right Moment to Reconsider Netflix After This 9.6% Drop?
summary: Thinking about what to do with your Netflix stock right now? You are not alone. Whether you already own shares or are eyeing the stock from the sidelines, the recent moves have surely grabbed your attention. Netflix is a company that just keeps adapting and surprising investors, sending its stock price through dramatic swings with every new development in streaming, content strategy, or even international expansion. After a blazing rally to start the year, with shares up 23.5% year-to-date...
